HEADWORD: Tisri
<hw>Tis"ri</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Heb.
<ets>tishr⟦imac⟧</ets>, fr. Chald. <ets>sher⟦amac⟧'</ets> to open, to
